{"tid":1234322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一句講晒 各有各做，槍口對外","createTime":"2019-06-17T01:38:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T05:44:38.000Z","uid":19255,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"52be9c9afb402bc1ed7025b52d0685cd775bf118","tid":1234322,"uid":19255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:38:16.000Z","msg":"雖然依家主流係民意戰，個人亦認為依家唔係衝嘅好時機，但所有野都有正反兩邊，話唔定會有意外收穫<br />\n<br />\n請停止分化，勿忘初心<br />\n不割蓆，不篤灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c15a72b37e5188362925be78ade3650e7f9f083","tid":1234322,"uid":40763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:39:14.000Z","msg":"而家走 讚成<br />\n但係諗一諗 各有各做<br />\n只要佢地堅持 我就支持<br />\n民意我地可以幫佢打返來<br />\n可以同屋企人 同身邊既人解釋<br />\n結果係點唔知 但係佢地真人為香港<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">永不篤灰 永不割𥱊</span></span>"},{"pid":"7a7d58479b0c0991ea690195f42ddeefcd3fd74e","tid":1234322,"uid":19255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:47:06.000Z","msg":"依家嘅成功好大部份係歸功於我地嘅團結<br />\n有啲唔開心嘅野發生左就算啦<br />\n有時間去拗不如諗吓下次出去點保護自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8db3464c305b23637a404e4645749cac2e3b3c5","tid":1234322,"uid":91319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:38:39.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n呢個時候唔好分化"},{"pid":"9479efb440431d6fac20fa652a720e5c5ac9fc04","tid":1234322,"uid":231040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:39:52.000Z","msg":"【反送中過後】屌你老味!!! 下星期就係《國歌法》二讀嘞....<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cPCuxS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cPCuxS</a>"},{"pid":"a0173e5464ab95611e84cd0fed09cbd50b19b4b3","tid":1234322,"uid":134206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T05:41:33.000Z","msg":"KO左賤種警犬同林鄭先嘈啦"},{"pid":"029ef61ee39a44437a63837e3db3cc5544615c6e","tid":1234322,"uid":19255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quot